{
  "stem": "1282.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Should I go on?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, a cousin of mine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a cousin of mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the first story--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first story was mine, that because we had lice, we had typhoid fever, which, you know, so many people died after especially Dachau.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So many people died after liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And about a week or so-- now, we were liberated April the 9th-- the 29th.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And about a week later, I just collapsed on the street and I passed out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember no more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember anything after that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the only thing that I remember that happened to me, that I woke up sometimes, somewheres, where I saw as if I were on clouds and everything is-- is white.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whatever I see, a white-- white room, everything's just a white-- I could not distinguish what it was.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in my mind, subconsciously, somehow, that this must be death-like.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm floating on a cloud.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I must be dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, this has been already 10, 15 days that has gone by since I collapsed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I moved and a German nurse passed by and she screamed, Herr Doctor!",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[GERMAN] I mean, Doctor, come quickly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Doctor came over to me, and I passed out again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't remember what has happened afterwards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The next thing I remember, that I woke up and I-- my eyes were blur, completely blurred.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I didn't know where I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I saw like a huge sunburst, which started coming into focus slowly, slowly, slowly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I realize that I'm somewheres.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the sunburst got smaller.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I realize this is a carnation I'm looking at.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there's a nurse sitting next to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she says, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Happy birthday.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was June 4.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
